title: Tumi Alpha Bravo Kingsville Deluxe Brief Pack 0222382AT2 - Overview
description:
Tumi Navy Alpha Bravo Kingsville Deluxe Brief Pack - 222382 - NAVY
http://www.abt.com/product/97894/Tumi-222382NAVY.html

From our Bravo collection of modern unstructured day and travel bags comes this deluxe backpack ideal for professionals and students. It features numerous organizer pockets inside and out as well as dedicated space for a laptop and iPad. Exterior pockets include a waterproof pocket for a water bottle or umbrella. Made from a durable fabric with a top carry handle comfortable and adjustable backpack strap and a 3D mesh padded back. Easy zip access to main compartment.
Features:
• Primary Material: Ballistic Nylon 
• Interior:
o iPad pocket
o Laptop pocket
o 2 zip pockets
o 3 media pockets
o Pen loops
o 1 business card pocket
o 1 open pocket
o Key leash
• Exterior:
o Add-a-Bag sleeve
o Webbing top carry handle with leather accent
o Zip entry to main compartments
o Front and side U-zip pockets
o Quick access back pocket
o Luggage tag
o Multiple organizer pockets
